org.junit.experimental.theories.ParametersSuppliedBy

  • Packages that use ParametersSuppliedBy 
    Package Description
    org.junit.experimental.theories  
    org.junit.experimental.theories.suppliers  

    • Uses of ParametersSuppliedBy in org.junit.experimental.theories

      Classes in org.junit.experimental.theories with annotations of type ParametersSuppliedBy 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      interface  FromDataPoints
      Annotating a parameter of a @Theory method with @FromDataPoints will limit the datapoints considered as potential values for that parameter to just the DataPoints with the given name.

    • Uses of ParametersSuppliedBy in org.junit.experimental.theories.suppliers

      Classes in org.junit.experimental.theories.suppliers with annotations of type ParametersSuppliedBy 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      interface  TestedOn
      Annotating a Theory method int parameter with @TestedOn causes it to be supplied with values from the ints array given when run as a theory by the Theories runner.
